    "description": "《Champions of Chaos》领主包为《Total War: WARHAMMER III》添加了四名可游玩的传奇领主，在混沌魔域与超凡帝国战役中皆可使用<br><br>扮演『血腥』瓦尔基娅、『水蛭领主』费斯图斯、诅咒亲王阿扎泽尔与『诅咒灵』维里奇在战役中一统天下。这些领主在WARHAMMER III的混沌魔域与超凡帝国战役中皆可使用。不过，他们都有各自独特的战役机制与目标，不会参与混沌魔域中的厄孙剧情<br><br>随着时间的推移，玩家可以将低阶凡人部队（如掠夺者）升阶为黑暗诸神的强大奴仆，例如混沌骑士与神选者。混沌领主与英雄亦可一路擢升为恶魔亲王，甚至直接为黑暗诸神之一效命<br><br>•\t4位全新的传奇领主可供体验…<br>•\t…各自具有以混沌为背景的全新战役机制<br>•\t超凡帝国与混沌魔域战役中皆可游玩《Champions of Chaos》<br>•\t50余种全新的战场部队<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/f83168edb31ea071383f2955ef31fac4.avif?t=1763647978\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/36559619b33622b555f76d33fd2ed16a.avif?t=1763647978\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>恐虐新娘『血<br>腥』瓦尔基娅将以血神之名降临世间、大肆屠戮。瓦尔基娅的杀戮机制与恐虐有所不同，其奖励更符合鲜血女王的欲求。此外，她的派系还会在战斗获胜后获得战役地图移动距离加成<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/d240af99b0d76c0da36144370dbf0df2.poster.avif?t=1763647978\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/d240af99b0d76c0da36144370dbf0df2.webm?t=1763647978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/d240af99b0d76c0da36144370dbf0df2.mp4?t=1763647978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/fd2abb7d4bc52440188d01507578255c.avif?t=1763647978\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>&quot;费斯图斯曾是一名技艺精湛的医生。怜悯之心令他误入歧途，用自己的灵魂与理智换来了拯救他人的学识<br>不再受伦理道德束缚的『水蛭领主』将以纳垢的名义培育瘟疫。他收集瘟疫配料的方式有别于其他恶魔同伴，但药剂的功效绝不会因此而逊色&quot;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/69bf18211a2b05d948aa4ec9a6fd44de.poster.avif?t=1763647978\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/69bf18211a2b05d948aa4ec9a6fd44de.webm?t=1763647978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/69bf18211a2b05d948aa4ec9a6fd44de.mp4?t=1763647978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/4fe6f572df068c1f2c1b21bb4ce9f83f.avif?t=1763647978\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>&quot;据称阿扎泽尔的美貌仅次于他的主人色孽，大多数对手甚至在战斗开始之间便已倒戈卸甲…有谁能忍心伤害如此精妙迷人的尤物呢？<br>这便是阿扎泽尔的魅力所在，他能够利用色孽的诱惑机制在战前勾引敌人投诚。而那些被他击败的人，则会被刻上他的独特印记：阿扎泽尔印记&quot;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/44d06825aaa32da3693af32fa09c7a75.poster.avif?t=1763647978\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/44d06825aaa32da3693af32fa09c7a75.webm?t=1763647978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/44d06825aaa32da3693af32fa09c7a75.mp4?t=1763647978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/22abc0d4731ee502dd25bb56f4d2a29a.avif?t=1763647978\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>&quot;畸形怪诞的双子巫师维里奇把自己的魔法能力与哥哥的强壮身躯合为一体，将那些胆敢反对他的人尽数奴役<br>维里奇可以和其他奸奇同伴一样使用各种万变之道，并且开局便拥有对敌人进行传送攻击的能力&quot;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/41ce580596a6f90f0acdb3652d3817ff.poster.avif?t=1763647978\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/41ce580596a6f90f0acdb3652d3817ff.webm?t=1763647978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824060/extras/41ce580596a6f90f0acdb3652d3817ff.mp4?t=1763647978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
